T1  - Scientific Management in the U.S.S.R., With Particular Reference to the Contribution of Walter N. Polakov
AU  - Wren, Daniel A.
Y1  - 1980/01/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1980.4288834
